'''Nerfscourge''' was a type of flower that contained pollen which, if overused, was capable of causing nerve damage to most [[Species/Legends|species]]. [[Lumiya]] used it as a trap in her [[Apartment three hundred seven twelve|apartment]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]].

